features: [Precise And Stable Power Supply] PC motherboard's power supply is stable and precise, evenly distributed, and the thermal load of various power supply chipsets improves CPU performance. Multi phase power supply, stable and durable.
[Premium Materials] ATX motherboard with premium PCB material, rugged, all solid state panel, long service life. 225 x 175mm size, fine workmanship, to ensure a close fit installation.

[High Speed] Computer motherboard with NVME M.2 interface, full speed M.2 hard drive interface, M.2 support 32GB/s data transfer speed, for the operating system and application drivers of the best choice.
[Multi Interface] Dual channel DDR4 DIMM, supporting up to 64GB, PCI E 16X Gen 3.0 slot, PCIE 3.0 X1 expansion slot, HD Multimedia Interface, VGA video interface, Gigabit Ethernet and 5.1 HD sound.
[Compatible Processor] B365 desktop computer motherboard, support for Intel 6 7 8 9 generation, for Core i3 i5 i7 and for Celeron, for Pentium processors, fully meet your replacement use needs.
